      "notes": "Fill this in before the first signed aggregation. Derive the public key from DESKMODAL_SIGNING_KEY (the Ed25519 private key secret used by every plugin repo's release workflow) via: python3 -c 'from cryptography.hazmat.primitives.asymmetric.ed25519 import Ed25519PrivateKey; import os; k=Ed25519PrivateKey.from_private_bytes(bytes.fromhex(os.environ[\"DESKMODAL_SIGNING_KEY\"])); print(k.public_key().public_bytes_raw().hex())'"
    }
  },
